		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Hawala</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For the community in the Arab Gulf states, see <a href="/wiki/Huwala" title="Huwala">Huwala</a>.</div>
<p><b>Hawala</b> (also known as <b>hundi</b>) is an <a href="/wiki/Informal_value_transfer_system" title="Informal value transfer system">informal value transfer system</a> based on the performance and honor of a huge network of money brokers, which are primarily located in the <a href="/wiki/Near_East" title="Near East">Near East</a>, <a href="/wiki/North_Africa" title="North Africa">North</a> and <a href="/wiki/Northeast_Africa" title="Northeast Africa" class="mw-redirect">Northeast Africa</a>, and <a href="/wiki/South_Asia" title="South Asia">South Asia</a>.</p>
